Interpretation
The MUC F1 of 0.197 is deceptively low. MUC only gets credit for correctly linked pairs; since most gold clusters in this dataset are singletons or pairs with exactly one link, the denominator is very small and any mis-link hits hard. The model gets near-perfect B³ (0.942) and CEAFe (0.933) because mention identity is almost entirely correct — the 4 merge errors are the only real mistakes across 20 documents.
